       P200-FETCH-CURSOR-CURCCIN.
     š*****************************************************************
     š*-
           EXEC SQL FETCH CURCCIN
                     INTO
                       :BPCJCCIN.IDCONT
                     , :BPCJCCIN.IDINST
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE SQLCODE  TO  W-SQLCODE, W-EDTSQLC.

           EVALUATE TRUE
