             MOVE IDCONT OF BPCJCCIN  TO WS-IDCONT
             MOVE IDINST OF BPCJCCIN  TO WS-IDINST
     š*-
           WHEN SQLCODE-NOTFOUND
              SET  FIM-P001          TO TRUE
           WHEN OTHER
              SET   FIM-P001         TO TRUE
              MOVE "CURCCIN"         TO W-OBJECT-NAME
              SET   CMD-FETCH-CURSOR TO TRUE
              PERFORM  P990-ERRO-DB2
           END-EVALUATE.
