       P300-PROCESSO-GERAL.
     š*****************************************************************
     š*-
     š*-  Obtem Informação Financeira Instrumentos
           IF SQLCODE-OK
              PERFORM P400-CALL-BPCSPFIN
           END-IF.
     š*- Trata Intervenientes
           IF SQLCODE-OK
              PERFORM P400-CALL-BPCSPFIN1
           END-IF.
     š*- Trata Protecções
