     š*----------------------------------------------------------------
       P400-CALL-BPCSPFIN.
     š*----------------------------------------------------------------
           INITIALIZE              BPCBPFIN-LKPARMS.
           MOVE IDCONT OF BPCJCCIN TO BPCBPFIN-IDCONT
           MOVE IDINST OF BPCJCCIN TO BPCBPFIN-IDINST
           MOVE WS-RACINE-INST     TO BPCBPFIN-RACINE
           MOVE WS-GRE-INST        TO BPCBPFIN-CPGRE
           MOVE WS-RUB-INST        TO BPCBPFIN-CPRUB
           MOVE WS-MON-INST        TO BPCBPFIN-CPMON
           MOVE WS-CTR-CONT        TO BPCBPFIN-CTID
           MOVE WS-SEQ-CONT        TO BPCBPFIN-CTCONT
           MOVE WS-DTREF           TO BPCBPFIN-DTPROC

           CALL "BPCSPFIN" USING   BPCBPFIN-LKPARMS
           IF BPCBPFIN-PROC-OK
              CONTINUE
           ELSE
             SET  FIM-P001          TO TRUE
             INITIALIZE   KYCT900A
             MOVE BPCBPFIN-DESCERR  TO ERRMSG   OF  KYCT900A
             MOVE BPCBPFIN-CODERR   TO ERRCOD   OF  KYCT900A
             MOVE "BPCSPFIN"        TO ERRPRG   OF  KYCT900A
             MOVE "BPC"             TO ERRAPL   OF  KYCT900A
             MOVE BPCBPFIN-IDMSGEXE TO ERROBJ   OF  KYCT900A
             MOVE  1                TO ERRRTC   OF  KYCT900A
             PERFORM P995-INSERT-ERROS
           END-IF.
