                     ,  USERCRIA
                     ,  TMSALT
                     ,  USERALT
                     ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                 FROM  BPCJPFIN2
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE SQLCODE  TO  W-SQLCODE, W-EDTSQLC.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN SQLCODE-OK
             CONTINUE
           WHEN SQLCODE-NOTFOUND
             CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
              MOVE "BPCJHPFIN2"        TO W-OBJECT-NAME
              SET CMD-INSERT           TO TRUE
              PERFORM  P990-ERRO-DB2
           END-EVALUATE.
